
Testbed
=======

(1)
Install dependency:
- get GeoTools 8.5 (no other versions tested), <http://www.geotools.org/>
    geotools-8.5-bin.zip
- unpack into lib

cd project/lib
unzip ~/geotools-8.5-bin.zip

- search for all gt-epsg-*.jar

find . -name gt-epsg\*jar

- delete all of those but one (for example, keep gt-epsg-hsql-8.5.jar)

rm ./geotools-8.5/gt-epsg-oracle-8.5.jar
rm ./geotools-8.5/gt-epsg-wkt-8.5.jar
rm ./geotools-8.5/gt-epsg-extension-8.5.jar
rm ./geotools-8.5/gt-epsg-postgresql-8.5.jar

The class path consists of the lib directory and any _immediate_ subdirectories.

(2)
Install test dataset:

cd data/testbed
wget http://www.remote.org/frederik/tmp/nrw-roads.zip

- execute data/testbed/prepare-testdata.sh

./prepare-testdata.sh

(3)
Build and run:

cd project
./run-testbed.sh

(Ant needs the current working directory set to project/ !)


Notes:
- "'on the fly' CRS transformation" needs to be enabled in QGIS's Project Properties, otherwise QGIS will ignore any CRS specified in the data.



